NATIONAL RIFLE ASSOCIATION OF AMERICA, INC., petitioner,
v.
Steven C. McCRAW, in His Official Capacity as Director of the Texas Department of Public Safety. No. 13-390. Supreme Court of the United States Feb. 24, 2014.

Case below, 719 F.3d 338.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit denied.
